---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';

const description = "Brian Bricker — 20+ years running operations and improving how businesses work. Why AI Lean Solutions builds practical AI initiatives across education, workflow improvement, market intelligence, and technician support.";
---

<Base title="About" description={description}>

  <!-- Editorial hero — light mode, warm -->
  <section class="relative bg-paper-100 text-text-dark overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container-site relative pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24">

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1.4fr] gap-12 md:gap-16 items-start">

        <!-- Photo column -->
        <div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-paper-200 shadow-xl">
            <img
              src="/brand/brian-paris.jpg"
              alt="Brian Bricker, founder of AI Lean Solutions"
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
              width="800"
              height="1000"
              loading="eager"
              onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentNode.querySelector('.photo-fallback').style.display='grid';"
            />
            <div class="photo-fallback absolute inset-0 hidden place-items-center text-center p-8 bg-paper-200 text-text-dark/40">
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label">Placeholder</div>
                <p class="mt-2 text-[13px]">Drop <code>brian-paris.jpg</code> in <code>/public/brand/</code></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-text-dark/60">
            Brian Bricker · Founder &amp; CEO
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Story column -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-amber-accent mb-5">
            // Brian&rsquo;s story
          </p>
          <h1 class="font-display font-bold tracking-tightest text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.75rem)] leading-[1.02] text-text-dark">
            Twenty years running operations<br/>taught me one thing:
            <span class="italic font-normal">useful technology starts with the work people actually do.</span>
          </h1>

          <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-text-dark/80 max-w-prose">
            <p>
              I&rsquo;m Brian Bricker. I&rsquo;ve spent my career in process improvement, operations,
              and business leadership &mdash; two decades of walking into rooms where good people
              were working harder than they should because the process around them was unclear,
              manual, delayed, or built for somebody else&rsquo;s business.
            </p>
            <p>
              The pattern shows up everywhere. A small business owner knows the customer but not
              what the competitor changed last week. A field technician needs a second opinion
              while the job is still in front of them. A team keeps copying the same information
              between emails, notes, calendars, forms, and spreadsheets. Regular people hear
              breathless AI talk and still have no idea how to get one useful result.
            </p>
            <p>
              AI is not the answer to every problem. But used carefully, it can watch, summarize,
              draft, route, explain, and advise in places where small teams have never had enough
              time or support. That is the opening AI Lean Solutions is built around.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today the company is an umbrella for several practical AI initiatives: public AI
              education through AI Promotion Guy, workflow improvement through Rowan Vale and
              UsefulOps AI, weekly competitive intelligence for local businesses, and technical
              support pilots for field technicians. Different personalities, same standard:
              useful first, clear next, human judgment always.
            </p>
            <p class="font-display text-[19px] font-medium text-text-dark">
              &mdash; Brian
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <Section num="01" eyebrow="Mission">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1.3fr] gap-12 items-start">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold tracking-tightest text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.05]">
        Make practical AI useful to people who do not have a transformation department.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-[17px] leading-relaxed">
        Large companies can buy dashboards, consultants, analysts, trainers, and internal
        automation teams. Smaller businesses and regular working people usually get a tool,
        a login, and a shrug. AI Lean Solutions exists to close that practical-use gap with
        focused initiatives that help people understand AI, improve workflows, see the market
        more clearly, and get faster support when work is happening in real time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Initiatives -->
  <Section num="02" eyebrow="What we are building">
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold tracking-tightest text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.05] max-w-[22ch]">
      One umbrella. Four useful directions.
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-5 text-text-muted text-[17px] leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
      AI Lean Solutions is not trying to make one giant platform. The company builds focused
      initiatives where AI can create a real operational advantage without burying people in
      jargon or software theater.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="/ai-promotion-guy" class="card p-7 block">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-[#ffd23f] mb-4">Public AI adoption</div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">AI Promotion Guy</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Positive, practical AI education for everyday Americans and Main Street business owners
          who need their first useful AI win before they need a lecture.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a href="/usefulops-ai" class="card p-7 block">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-[#14b8a6] mb-4">Workflow improvement</div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">UsefulOps AI</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Rowan Vale&rsquo;s autonomous AI-owned and operated consulting business, built to help
          small businesses reduce admin drag and improve repeat workflows.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a href="/market-intelligence" class="card p-7 block">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-brand-cyan mb-4">Market intelligence</div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">Competitive Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Weekly plain-language reports that watch real local competitors and tell business owners
          what changed, why it matters, and what to consider next.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a href="/expert-technician" class="card p-7 block">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-[#fb923c] mb-4">Field technician support</div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">Expert Technician</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          A 24/7 technical and troubleshooting support pilot for US-based HVAC technicians, with
          real-time guidance and resources sent directly to email.
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <Section num="03" eyebrow="What we actually believe">
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold tracking-tightest text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.05] max-w-[22ch]">
      Straight talk, not marketing talk.
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-5 text-text-muted text-[17px] leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
      Three commitments. Short enough to remember, concrete enough to hold us to.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card p-7 relative">
        <span class="absolute top-5 right-5 font-mono text-[40px] leading-none text-brand-cyan/20">01</span>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Useful beats impressive.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          A small win someone can use today is worth more than a grand AI promise nobody can
          explain, trust, or maintain.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-7 relative">
        <span class="absolute top-5 right-5 font-mono text-[40px] leading-none text-brand-cyan/20">02</span>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Process before software.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          We start with the work: who needs what, when it gets stuck, what decision matters,
          and where AI can help without making the system more fragile.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-7 relative">
        <span class="absolute top-5 right-5 font-mono text-[40px] leading-none text-brand-cyan/20">03</span>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Human judgment stays in charge.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          AI can assist, draft, summarize, and advise. People still own trust, responsibility,
          taste, accountability, and final decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Company facts -->
  <Section num="04" eyebrow="Company">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-[14px]">
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-text-muted mb-1.5">Entity</div>
        <div class="font-display text-lg">AI Lean Solutions LLC</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-text-muted mb-1.5">Founded</div>
        <div class="font-display text-lg">2025</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-text-muted mb-1.5">Based</div>
        <div class="font-display text-lg">Sacramento, CA</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-text-muted mb-1.5">Status</div>
        <div class="font-display text-lg">Four active AI initiatives</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

</Base>
